\csdef{drawm}{
	\begin{scope}[every node/.style={anchor=north west, inner xsep=5mm, inner ysep=5mm, font=\sffamily\color{black!70}}]
		\foreach[count=\i] \g/\r/\t in \rlist{
			\node at (a\i) {\parbox{50mm}{%
				检测基因：\g \\[3mm]
				检测位点：\r \\[3mm]
				基因分型：\t
			}};
		}
	\end{scope}
}

\newcommand{\namem}[1]{%
	\foreach[count=\i] \position in {#1}{%
		\node (a\i) at \position {};
	}	
	\csuse{drawm}
}

\newcommand{\mrong}[2][red]{
	\gdef\rlist{#2}
	\foreach[count=\ii] \i in \rlist{\global\let\maxitem\ii}
	\definecolor{c4b69bb}{named}{#1}
%	\gdef\rlist{#2}
	\csuse{mrong\maxitem}
}
